main_body:
The following points (p), (q) and (r) shall be added to Article 2 of Regulation (Euratom, ECSC, EEC) No 549/69: "(p) those entitled to the allowance provided for in the event of termination of service under Article 4 of Regulation (EC, Euratom) No 1746/2002;
(q) those entitled to the allowance provided for in the event of termination of service under Article 4 of Regulation (EC, Euratom) No 1747/2002;
(r) those entitled to the allowance provided for in the event of termination of service under Article 4 of Regulation (EC, Euratom) No 1748/2002."
